description:
Welcome to the course on "Statistics Concepts - Sampling or Survey Sampling"
In this course students will learn basic and advance concepts of sampling .
After learn the course students will be able to apply sample surveys and they will learn the Numericals to solve the questions of sampling like how to find mean , sample mean? population mean and , sample variance , Standard Error Etc Etc with lot of Examples and PDF files . The students will know probability sampling, non-probability sampling, and sample survey theory.
Including Exercises and PDF Files for Practice .
So Enroll Today!
title: Statistics Concepts - Sampling or Survey Sampling
